for installation instructions please visit the Ergatis site:

http://ergatis.sourceforge.net/documentation/install_guide.html

Developers can also build from an SVN checkout or export

1)Add symlinks for bin/ and lib/
ln -s ../src/perl bin
ln -s ../lib lib

2)Run with LIVE_BUILD parameter
perl Makefile.PL LIVE_BUILD INSTALL_BASE=/tmp
make
make install


